high_descs: Turn right, walk forward then turn left head to the shelf on your left
Pick up the credit card on the shelf
Turn around to your left head to the side table in between the beds
Put the credit card on the side table
Turn around to to your left then head to the shelf on your right
Pick up the credit card on the shelf
Turn right then head to the side table in between two beds
Put the credit card on the right side edge of the side table
anns.task_desc: Put the two credit cards on the side table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the bed, then turn left and walk towards the wall, turn left again to face the wooden shelving unit on the wall.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the bottom middle shelf of the shelving unit.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the nightstand in between the two bed.
Put the credit card on the nightstand to the left of the pencil.
Turn around and walk out from in between the two beds, then turn right and walk up to the wooden shelving unit on the wall.
Pick up the blue credit card that is on the bottom middle shelf of the shelving unit
Turn around and walk back over to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Put the credit card on the nightstand to the right of the pencil.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn to the left, then the left again. Face the desk on the left side.
Pick up the credit card from the middle shelf.
Carry the credit card and turn around. Turn right in between the beds.
Place the credit card on the floor, just past the two beds, on the left side.
Turn around then turn right to locate another shelf.
Pick up the credit card from the bottom shelf.
Carry the credit card and turn around, then left to go in between the beds.
Place the credit card on the floor, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the floor.
